        <p begin="00:07:45.400" end="00:07:48.150" tts:direction="ltr">Tool tips are really important.</p>
        <p begin="00:07:48.150" end="00:07:50.030" tts:direction="ltr">Now, remember to cross your Ts,</p>
        <p begin="00:07:50.030" end="00:07:51.870" tts:direction="ltr">you're going to learn a little bit more on
<br />how to</p>
        <p begin="00:07:51.870" end="00:07:54.270" tts:direction="ltr">apply tool tips in the adventure guide,</p>
        <p begin="00:07:54.270" end="00:07:57.330" tts:direction="ltr">and I hope to see you crossing your Ts</p>
        <p begin="00:07:57.330" end="00:08:01.650" tts:direction="ltr">with takeaway titles and using tool tips.
